Privacy Notice :: Terms of Use :: Cookies Policy
© Missguided ltd // Official Babe Uniform
Cookie Settings
To offer you the best experience on our website www.missguided.co.uk (“Site”) we may sometimes track information about you using Cookies and similar technologies ("Cookies"). Cookies are used to help you navigate and use our Site efficiently and perform functions such as, experience enrichment, analytics, and targeting advertising. We recommend allowing Cookies to get the best experience when using our Site.
These Cookies are required for the safe operation of the Sites/App and use of all its features. For these Cookies we do not require your consent. They include, for example, Cookies that enable you to log into secure areas of the Site and use a shopping basket. If these are disabled then some of the necessary website functionality will be lost.
These are used to provide added functionality to our Sites/App, these Cookies are used to recognise you when you return to the Sites/App, the number of visitors to the Sites/App, where visitors have come from and the pages visited. This enables us to personalise our content for you, greet you by name and remember your preferences (for example, your choice of language or region). Such analysis may be conducted by third parties in which case they are considered as third party Cookies. In order to use these Cookies we require your consent.
These Cookies allow us to recognise and count the number of visitors and to see how visitors move around the Sites/App. This helps us to improve the way the Sites/App work, for example, by ensuring that users are finding what they are looking for easily. The Cookies collect information including the number of visitors to the Sites/App, where visitors have come to the Sites/App from, the pages they have visited and how long they visited the Sites/App. We use this information to compile reports and to help us improve the Sites/App. In order to use these Cookies we require your consent.
These Cookies are placed by third party advertising companies and collect information about your browsing habits in order to display advertising more relevant to your interests based on your online navigation. We may also share this information with third parties for this purpose or to inform our future marketing campaigns and target bases. For example, we use these Cookies to: • Show you interest-based advertising following a visit on our Website; • Provide third party advertising companies and social networks (such as Facebook or Twitter) information about your visit on our Website so that they can show you interest-based advertising; • Control advertising effectiveness through tracking lead conversion (track that you have made a purchase after following a link to our Website from another third party website). In order to use these Cookies we require your consent.
At Missguided we use our own and third-party cookies & tracking/similar technologies to give you the best shopping experience, you can find out more by visiting our Cookies Notice. You can manage your cookies & tracking/similar technologies here manage my cookies
